/waketask-ios/Packages/Localization/Sources/Localization/L10n+Onboarding.swift`\n- `apps/waketask-ios/Packages/Localization/Sources/Localization/L10n+Wake.swift`\n- `apps/waketask-ios/Packages/Localization/Sources/Localization/L10n+Profile.swift`\n- `apps/waketask-ios/Packages/Localization/Sources/Localization/L10n+Payments.swift`\n- `apps/waketask-ios/Packages/Localization/Sources/Localization/Resources/en.lproj/Localizable.strings`\n- `apps/waketask-ios/Packages/Localization/Sources/Localization/Resources/es.lproj/Localizable.strings`\n- `apps/waketask-ios/Packages/DesignSystem/Sources/DesignSystem/Tokens/DSColors.swift`\n- `apps/waketask-ios/Packages/DesignSystem/Sources/DesignSystem/Tokens/DSTypography.swift`\n- `apps/waketask-ios/Packages/DesignSystem/Sources/DesignSystem/Tokens/DSSpacing.swift`\n- `apps/waketask-ios/Packages/DesignSystem/Sources/DesignSystem/Tokens/DSRadius.swift`\n- `apps/waketask-ios/Packages/DesignSystem/Sources/DesignSystem/Components/SAIButton.swift`\n- `apps/waketask-ios/Packages/DesignSystem/Sources/DesignSystem/Components/SAICard.swift`\n- `apps/waketask-ios/Packages/DesignSystem/Sources/DesignSystem/Components/SAIListRow.swift`\n- `apps/waketask-ios/Packages/DesignSystem/Sources/DesignSystem/Components/SAISkeleton.swift`\n- `apps/waketask-ios/Packages/DesignSystem/Sources/DesignSystem/Accessibility/A11yModifiers.swift`\n- `apps/waketask-ios/SwiftAIBoilerplateProUITests/SwiftAIBoilerplateProUITests.swift`\n- `apps/waketask-ios/SwiftAIBoilerplateProUITests/IntegrationWakeExploratoryUITests.swift`\n- `apps/waketask-ios/SwiftAIBoilerplateProUITests/PaywallFlowUITests.swift`\n- `apps/waketask-ios/SwiftAIBoilerplateProUITests/AuthFlowUITests.swift`\n- `apps/waketask-ios/SwiftAIBoilerplateProTests/AppShellSnapshotTests.swift`\n- `apps/waketask-ios/SwiftAIBoilerplateProTests/HomeViewModelTests.swift`\n- `apps/waketask-ios/SwiftAIBoilerplateProTests/HomeContentTests.swift`\n- `apps/waketask-ios/SwiftAIBoilerplateProTests/WakeTask/WakeFlowViewModelTests.swift`\n- `apps/waketask-ios/Packages/FeatureSettings/Tests/FeatureSettingsTests/PaywallViewModelTests.swift`\n- `apps/waketask-ios/Packages/FeatureSettings/Tests/PaywallSnapshotTests.swift`\n- `apps/waketask-ios/scripts/qa/appium-exploratory-tapper.sh`\n- `apps/waketask-ios/README.md`\n\n## Existing App File Map\n- `SwiftAIBoilerplatePro/AppShell/AppRootView.swift`: top-level route + onboarding modal presentation + theme application.\n- `SwiftAIBoilerplatePro/AppShell/LaunchRouter.swift`: auth/onboarding gate and first-run routing policy.\n- `SwiftAIBoilerplatePro/AppShell/MainTabView.swift`: tab IA (`Home`/`Runs`/`Profile`), paywall/settings sheet entry points, root tab IDs.\n- `SwiftAIBoilerplatePro/AppShell/HomeView.swift`: current home layout (hero, quick actions, featured cards, recent runs list).\n- `SwiftAIBoilerplatePro/AppShell/HomeViewModel.swift`: home loading/error/quick-action orchestration.\n- `SwiftAIBoilerplatePro/AppShell/HomeContent.swift`: static quick-action and feature-card copy defaults.\n- `SwiftAIBoilerplatePro/AppShell/Wake/WakeDashboardView.swift`: list-based wake task list, create/edit sheet, active run controls, reliability rows, existing wake Appium IDs.\n- `SwiftAIBoilerplatePro/AppShell/Wake/WakeFlowViewModel.swift`: alarm/run lifecycle and state machine used by list/active/completion/history behavior.\n- `SwiftAIBoilerplatePro/AppShell/OnboardingContainerView.swift`: onboarding flow container, skip/next/get-started controls.\n- `SwiftAIBoilerplatePro/AppShell/OnboardingPageView.swift`: onboarding page visual treatment and motion behavior.\n- `SwiftAIBoilerplatePro/AppShell/OnboardingPage.swift`: onboarding content model/default pages.\n- `SwiftAIBoilerplatePro/AppShell/ProfileView.swift`: profile screen composition, settings/paywall launch paths, destructive action alerts.\n- `SwiftAIBoilerplatePro/AppShell/Profile/ProfileSubscriptionSection.swift`: subscription status + restore purchases action.\n- `SwiftAIBoilerplatePro/AppShell/Profile/ProfileQuickActionsSection.swift`: settings/help/legal rows.\n- `SwiftAIBoilerplatePro/AppShell/Profile/ProfileAccountInfoSection.swift`: account metadata rows.\n- `Packages/FeatureSettings/Sources/FeatureSettings/Views/PaywallView.swift`: paywall UI, plan selection, subscribe/restore actions, paywall Appium IDs.\n- `Packages/FeatureSettings/Sources/FeatureSettings/ViewModels/PaywallViewModel.swift`: paywall loading/purchase/restore behavior.\n- `Packages/FeatureSettings/Sources/FeatureSettings/Views/Settings/SettingsSubscriptionSection.swift`: secondary subscription entry point and restore action.\n- `Packages/Localization/Sources/Localization/L10n+Onboarding.swift`: onboarding localization accessors.\n- `Packages/Localization/Sources/Localization/L10n+Wake.swift`: wake flow/list/reliability/a11y localization accessors.\n- `Packages/Localization/Sources/Localization/L10n+Profile.swift`: profile localization accessors.\n- `Packages/Localization/Sources/Localization/L10n+Payments.swift`: paywall/subscription localization accessors.\n- `Packages/Localization/Sources/Localization/Resources/en.lproj/Localizable.strings`: English string values.\n- `Packages/Localization/Sources/Localization/Resources/es.lproj/Localizable.strings`: Spanish string values.\n- `Packages/DesignSystem/Sources/DesignSystem/Tokens/DSColors.swift`: app-level color tokens.\n- `Packages/DesignSystem/Sources/DesignSystem/Tokens/DSTypography.swift`: typography tokens and semantic text styles.\n- `Packages/DesignSystem/Sources/DesignSystem/Tokens/DSSpacing.swift`: spacing tokens.\n- `Packages/DesignSystem/Sources/DesignSystem/Tokens/DSRadius.swift`: corner-radius tokens.\n- `Packages/DesignSystem/Sources/DesignSystem/Components/SAIButton.swift`: reusable primary/secondary button styling.\n- `Packages/DesignSystem/Sources/DesignSystem/Components/SAICard.swift`: card container pattern.\n- `Packages/DesignSystem/Sources/DesignSystem/Components/SAIListRow.swift`: reusable settings/list row